<hr class="help">

<br><br>
<a name="transaction_feedback_details"></a>
<h3>Transaction feedback details<br>
Set transaction feedback</h3>
Here you can enter or view the
<a href="#top"><u>feedback</u></a>
on a transaction. In the upper part, you see the Payment details. You can use
the hyperlinks to go to the member's
<a href="${pagePrefix}profiles"><u>profile</u></a>
. In the lower part, you can enter or view the feedback.
<br><br>If you happen to be the buyer, then you can enter feedback here. To enter
feedback, you have to select a value from the drop-down list and enter a
personal comment in the field &quot;Comments&quot;. Be careful: you cannot
change the feedback after submitting it. Click the &quot;Submit&quot; button to
finish.
<br><br>The seller can reply to your feedback. When that happens, you will see
the reply in this screen. <br>
If you are the seller, then you will have the option to enter a reply here, if
you did not already do so.
<br><br>The administration can comment on buyer and seller feedback, for instance
as a dispute resolution. 
<span class="member">
If the administrator did so, ou will see their comment
in the &quot;Administrator comments&quot; section.
</span>
<span class="admin">
You can enter your comment as administrator in the &quot;Administrator comments&quot; section
(don't forget to click the &quot;change&quot; button first, and to click &quot;submit&quot;
to save the entry when you're done).
</span>
